						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken stone built into the bund called sthāpane of the Varadā river in front of the Gaḷagēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary and damaged record seems to describe the valour of a hero (name lost). The divisions of <hi rend="bold">Kadambaḷige</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Gaṅga-maṇḍala</hi> are mentioned.</p>						

						<p>The characters belong to the <hi rend="bold">10-11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
